{
  "stem": "1736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he, with a number of other men, tried to cross the Belgian border to-- to get out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately-- and this was a-- he wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were thousands of people trying to get out from all sorts of borders.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In his case, it just happened to be the Belgian border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they got caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They got caught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the border police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German border police.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After being interrogated, the local guy who was in charge decided that-- seeing that my father was the only one amongst the guys there who had a Polish passport, even though it was expired-- he--",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He couldn't keep him because he was a foreign national.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, he-- that was in-- he was quite wrong because in fact, he was more wanted than the German passport-holders, Jewish German passport-- you understand what I'm saying?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he let him go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With that, he disappeared again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- just something came to my mind then that--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's relevant, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just came to my mind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had a gold-fob watch with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so that he wouldn't get caught and be accused of trying to smuggle gold out of the country, he went and threw that watch onto that wagon that was transporting them.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't know how the story-- how the whole thing went, but after the war, somehow he got this-- you know, there was some connection made that the watch came home, and we got that watch back.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I still have it today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've got no idea how this person that knew-- knew where to send it to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I've still got it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that just came back to my mind because we were talking about the reasons for-- for escaping.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, he then went back to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
